## Database Standards

### Prisma Model

```prisma
model User {
  id        String   @id @default(cuid())
  email     String   @unique
  password  String
  name      String
  role      Role     @default(USER)
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
  updatedAt DateTime @updatedAt
  posts     Post[]

  @@index([email])
  @@map("users")
}

enum Role {
  USER
  ADMIN
}
```

### Query Optimization

```typescript
// Use select to only choose needed fields
const user = await prisma.user.findUnique({
  where: { id },
  select: {
    id: true,
    email: true,
    name: true
  }
});

// Use include to load related data
const userWithPosts = await prisma.user.findUnique({
  where: { id },
  include: {
    posts: {
      take: 10,
      orderBy: { createdAt: 'desc' }
    }
  }
});

// Batch operations
await prisma.user.createMany({
  data: users
});
```

